title: Have A Spirit Of Excellence | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Have A Spirit Of Excellence | Joel Osteen
description:
When you live with a spirit of excellence, God will increase your favor and influence. Don’t settle for doing the bare minimum. When you do your part to pursue your dreams, God will take care of promoting you.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
